            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 10-29-99 10:11 PM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">I am on the web now, doing my daily check of Pez websites for the latest Pez news and such, and was just thinking about how glad I am that others are so nice to post on the web and keep stuff updated - it is what really help me enjoy the hobby.</font>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">So here are my specific kudos - first, to Jaime, for this website, which I adore - for this forum, the database, the links. In my mind, the best Pez resource on the net.</font></p>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Secondly, to Michel, the Pezpimp, &lt;www.globalserve.net/~pezcondo/&gt; for maintaining the fantastic new updates page, which is where I get all of my hot new Pez news. I check his page daily - it is THE place to get the latest Pez gossip.</font></p>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Thanks to you both. and please, fellow Pezheads, feel free to add some other thank yous. I know this hobby wouldn't be so much fun for me if it wasn't for the work people put into maintaining such good quality Pez webpages.</font></p>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">pezjenny</font></p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
          <td width="18%" valign="top"><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><b>juliej</b></font></td>
          <td>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial"><font size="1" color="#000080" face="Verdana, Arial">posted 11-02-99 02:30 AM CT (US)</font></font>
            <hr>
            <font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Someone recently posted a link in the forum to Spectres Pez Page at [url] http://members.aol.com/Spectres/index.html[/url]</font>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">It's the best collection site I've ever seen. The owner, Rob, has been collecting for over 23 years and describes with words & pics the amazing array of Pez variations he's ammassed. It's very cool to see all those pez and to figure out which variations I have.</font></p>
            <p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">Thanks</font></p>
          </td>
